title: Is the NFL a passing league or a rushing league?
text:
When you think of the modern NFL, what players do you think of? Most of the time, people think of elite passing quarterbacks or wide receivers or running backs.

title: About
text: My name is Josiah Dames and I am a Sports Media major at the University of Lincoln-Nebraska. I am a sports reporter for The Daily Nebraskan and Unlimited Sports and I am a part of a NFL podcast on YouTube. I am a huge fan of both college and pro football.
